bilingual.target: 燃气泄漏是非常危险的。

bilingual.source: A gas leak can be very dangerous.
bilingual.target: 瓦斯泄漏可能非常危险。

bilingual.source: A coal gas leak is very dangerous.
bilingual.target: 煤气泄漏是非常危险的。

bilingual.source: They found a leak in the furnace tube.
bilingual.target: 他们发现了炉管的泄漏。

bilingual.source: The gas leak caused the stove to explode.
bilingual.target: 煤气泄漏导致炉子爆炸。

bilingual.source: The gas leak caused a flaring fire.
bilingual.target: 煤气泄漏引起了突然燃烧的火焰。

bilingual.source: A gas leak can release carbon monoxide.
bilingual.target: 煤气泄漏可能会释放一氧化碳。

bilingual.source: The gas leak caused the building to explode.
bilingual.target: 煤气泄漏导致建筑物爆炸。

bilingual.source: The roof started to leak after the heavy rain.
bilingual.target: 大雨过后，屋顶开始泄漏。

bilingual.source: There was a carbonyl chloride leak in the factory.
bilingual.target: 工厂里发生了光气泄漏。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I don't know. We'll make up some story, and then we'll leak it. You were loyal, you did it for me. You were too loyal.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我说不好。我们会编一些事出来，然后泄漏出去。你忠心耿耿，你那么做是为了我。你忠诚过了头。

yingyinNormal.en: I need an outsider who won't leak. $500 an hour.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我需要一个能守口如瓶的局外人。五百美金一小时。

yingyinNormal.en: I need an investigator who won't leak. Who won't hurt Alicia.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我需要一个口风紧的调查员，还不会做出伤害她的事。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I would trace it to the Edward Snowden leak around June 10.
yingyinNormal.zh: 可以追溯到斯诺登泄密事件，六月十日左右吧。

yingyinNormal.en: Who do you think orchestrated that leak? Seems to know quite a lot.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不然你以为是谁泄的密？看来他知道的不少啊。

yingyinNormal.en: What did you do? What does it look like? I sprung a leak! There's gotta be a water shut-off.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你干了什么？你觉得呢？我把水管弄坏了！一定有阀门能关掉它的！

yingyinNormal.en: What? The gas is odorless, but they add the smell so you know when there's a leak. Well, okay.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？瓦斯其实是无色无味，加上味道是为了让人在瓦斯漏气时能闻得出来。

yingyinNormal.en: What? I'm the leak. I've been feeding information to Tom Hammerschmidt for months with Doug's help.
yingyinNormal.zh: 什么？我就是泄密者。这几个月我一直在道格的帮助下给汤姆·汉默施密特放料。

yingyinNormal.en: We can be sure of nothing, Francis. Everything going on with Doug, the leak still in the White House, No, that was me, too.
yingyinNormal.zh: 世事难料，弗兰西斯。道格的事，白宫还有泄密者，不 ，那也是我。

yingyinNormal.en: For now, they remain confidential. We cannot afford a leak to the press. There's been far too much talk in the press already.
yingyinNormal.zh: 目前数据暂时保密，我们还不能向媒体披露，这件事受到的关注实在是太大了。

yingyinNormal.en: A false story so that we can explain how we got our information that has nothing to do with Enigma. And then you can leak those stories to the Germans.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们就能解释情报的来源，而不是通过恩尼格玛得来的。你可以将这些谎言透露给德国人。

yingyinNormal.en: Hey Mr. Treeger, it's Joey Tribbiani. Listen, I need to get into Monica and Chandler's apartment. It's an emergency. Gas leak. Yeah oh, and bring garlic bread.
yingyinNormal.zh: 崔格先生？我是乔伊崔比亚尼，听着，我得到莫妮卡跟钱德家去，有紧急事件，瓦斯漏气，带大蒜面包过来。

yingyinNormal.en: All calls, e-mails, messages in and out of the White House will be monitored and archived. Every phone call will be recorded as we search for the leak. Video surveillance?
yingyinNormal.zh: 所有电话，电邮和短信进出白宫的一切通讯都会被监控归档。搜索泄露源期间每通电话都会被录音。视频监控呢？

yingyinNormal.en: Once the news of his Alzheimer's gets out, which it will, because no matter how much we all try to lie about it, it's gonna leak, can you imagine what that's going to do to his reputation?
yingyinNormal.zh: 一旦他患病的消息泄露，这总会泄露的，因为无论我们怎么说谎隐瞒它，总会传出去，你能想象那对他的名誉会造成什么影响吗？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。
